          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yet he was merciful and forgave their sins and did not destroy them all. Many times he held back his anger and did not unleash his fury! "
        }
