          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 62,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He gave his people over to be butchered by the sword, because he was so angry with his own people—his special possession. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
